==History==
*[[0.27]] Added [[Manifold Assault]]. Removed [[Gell's Gravitas]], [[Teleport Other]] and [[Passage of Golubria]] from the book. Prior to this version, this was the starting book for [[Warper]]s. For all classes with magic, starting books were replaced by sets of spells.
*Prior to [[0.20]], this book contained [[Portal Projectile]] instead of [[Gell's Gravitas]].
*Prior to [[0.19]], this book contained [[Apportation]] instead of [[Lesser Beckoning]].
*Prior to [[0.12]], this book also contained [[Control Teleport]].
